mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#000099;background:white">1. Way2SMS users are
not allowed to send SMS between 9PM to 9AM</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
color:black;background:white"><o:p></o:p></span></p>

</div>

<div>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:16.5pt"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;
