mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#000099;background:white">2. Way2SMS cannot
deliver your messages to your friends who are on <span class="GramE">DND(</span>do
not disturb) registry.</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white"><o:p></o:p></span></p>

