&nbsp;TRAI has categorized messages as Transactional and Promotional.
Unfortunately, they haven't addressed "<strong>Personal Messaging</strong>"
category. This made us to fall under<span class="apple-converted-space"><span style="font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></span><strong>Promotional
messaging</strong><span class="apple-converted-space"><span style="font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
